# Design System

## Typography Rules (HARD RULES)

### BANNED Classes (cause synthetic bolding)
- `font-bold` (700) -- BANNED
- `font-semibold` (600) -- BANNED
- `font-extrabold` (800) -- BANNED
- `font-black` (900) -- BANNED

Maximum allowed weight: `font-medium` (500)

### ALLOWED Classes
- `font-light` (300)
- `font-normal` (400)
- `font-medium` (500) -- MAXIMUM

### Font Families
| Class | Font | Usage | Rules |
|-------|------|-------|-------|
| `font-display` | Termina | Headlines, buttons, stats, navigation | Always uppercase, wide tracking (0.08em) |
| `font-sans` | Aeonik Pro | Body text, paragraphs, UI labels | NEVER uppercase |
| `font-serif` | Laguna | Editorial accents | Bold weight available |
| `font-script` | Sloop Script | Decorative elements | Use sparingly |

### Emphasis Without Bold

When you need visual hierarchy:
- Use `font-display` for headlines (automatic uppercase + tracking)
- Increase font size (`text-lg`, `text-xl`, `text-2xl`)
- Use color contrast (`text-foreground` vs `text-muted-foreground`)
- Add letter-spacing (`tracking-wide`, `tracking-wider`)
- Use borders or backgrounds for visual separation

### Quick Reference
```
BAD:  className="text-2xl font-bold"
GOOD: className="text-2xl font-medium"

BAD:  className="font-semibold text-foreground"
GOOD: className="font-medium text-foreground"

Headlines:  className="font-display text-2xl"
Body emphasis: className="font-medium text-foreground"
```

## Theme System

HSL CSS variables. Available themes:
- **Cream** (default) -- Light cream palette
- **Rose** -- Blush pink pastel
- **Sage** -- Mint green pastel
- **Ocean** -- Soft blue pastel
- **Platform** -- Purple/violet fintech-inspired (platform admin only)

Semantic colors: `primary`, `secondary`, `accent`, `destructive`, `success`, `oat`, `gold`

## Component Styling

- Always use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` to merge Tailwind classes
- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/`
- Dashboard content: `<div className="px-8 py-8 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">`

## Loading States

Spinner (full page):
```tsx
<div className="flex items-center justify-center h-64">
  <Loader2 className="h-8 w-8 animate-spin text-muted-foreground" />
</div>
```

Skeleton (tables/cards):
```tsx
{[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map((i) => (
  <Skeleton key={i} className="h-14 w-full" />
))}
```

## Empty States

Centered icon + heading + description:
```tsx
<div className="text-center py-12 text-muted-foreground">
  <Package className="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4" />
  <h3 className="font-medium text-lg mb-2">No items found</h3>
  <p className="text-sm">Try adjusting your filters</p>
</div>
```
